OL,3,CMSPs suspend former Scottish Health
OL,4,CSecretary over #11,000 iPad bill
OL,6,FITV News Scotland Reporter Louise
OL,7,FScott has the latest after Scottish
OL,8,FHealth Secretary Michael Matheson was
OL,9,Fsuspended over an #11,000 iPad roaming
OL,10,Fbill
OL,12,FMSPs have voted to suspend former
OL,13,FScottish Health Secretary Michael
OL,14,FMatheson for 27 days and strip him of
OL,15,Fhis salary for 54 days over an #11,000
OL,16,FiPad roaming bill.
OL,18,FMatheson has insisted he will remain
OL,19,Fan MSP, despite a vote of 64 to zero
OL,20,Fimposing tough sanctions on him.
