OL,3,CMSPs suspend former Scottish Health
OL,4,CSecretary over #11,000 iPad bill
OL,6,FThe row was originally sparked when Mr
OL,7,FMatheson admitted his teenage sons
OL,8,Fused his iPad as a hotspot so they
OL,9,Fcould watch football while on a family
OL,10,Fholiday in Morocco.
OL,12,FThe then-minister had initially
OL,13,Finsisted the device had only been used
OL,14,Ffor work purposes and he attempted to
OL,15,Fget the public purse to pick up the
OL,16,Fcosts.
OL,18,FHe later confessed to his children's
OL,19,Finvolvement, and paid the money back
OL,20,Fto the Scottish Parliament.
