OL,6,FWhile he later quit as health
OL,7,Fsecretary, he remains the MSP for
OL,8,FFalkirk West.
OL,10,FAn SNP amendment highlighting the
OL,11,Fparty's concerns that the committee,
OL,12,Fwhich recommended the sanctions had
OL,13,Fbeen prejudiced, "thereby bringing the
OL,14,FParliament into disrepute", was also
OL,15,Fpassed.
