OL,6,FIn a statement on Wednesday, Mr
OL,7,FMatheson said: "I apologise and regret
OL,8,Fthat this situation occurred. I
OL,9,Facknowledge and accept the decision of
OL,10,FParliament.
OL,12,F"I also note that Parliament has
OL,13,Fcalled for the Scottish Parliament
OL,14,FCorporate Body to carry out an
OL,15,Findependent review of the Parliament's
OL,16,Fcomplaints process to restore
OL,17,Fintegrity and confidence in the
OL,18,FParliament and its procedures, which I
OL,19,Fhope will be progressed.
